column5: I am looking for a digital map of Lac Seul that maps islands, hazardous areas, fishing hotspots, etc. Does anyone know where I can find this? I have checked Navionics and Garmin and have not found anything I can pre-load. Is anyone interested in sharing their waypoints? Our camp is near Ear Falls, ON.
try this: http://toporama.ctis.nrcan.gc.ca/ its canadian government topo maps, you can click and read the lat lon
If I was you I'd leave your GPS at home and just follow the guy in the Tracker. That way you can have the time of your life and an education all in the same week!
